{"tid":1146342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"葵涌16歲少女墮樓亡","createTime":"2019-05-09T07:39:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-10T02:24:07.000Z","uid":20933,"like":80,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"7dbe37f1f4b189ce0eac309544732afdb3682a90","tid":1146342,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T07:39:08.000Z","msg":"葵涌大廈街葵賢苑葵謙閣，早上10時45分，警方接報一名女子從高處墮下。救護員到場將事主送仁濟醫院搶救，但告不治，警方經調查後獲悉女事主姓陳，年僅16歲，警方沒有撿獲遺書，初步調查相信陳女從上址一樓層墮下，事件沒有可疑，死因有待驗屍後確定。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=oAUO7kpDmgkuxlfprI4EYRZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=a6708b8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a>"},{"pid":"9743c940386d8cbae476b4ba7c66c343fa873477","tid":1146342,"uid":20933,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T07:39:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190509/59580578\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190509%2F59580578&d=oAUO7kpDmgkuxlfprI4EYRZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=3d282470\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190509%2F59580578&h=8f3b83f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190509/59580578</a>"},{"pid":"b7511b6c3d67be4f1d2502ea4f33c72eee1a49bc","tid":1146342,"uid":10692,"like":41,"dislike":139,"score":-98,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T07:40:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9c3f86dda45219a0121bd3fcb60140cd5344ddea","tid":1146342,"uid":213877,"like":119,"dislike":6,"score":113,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T07:41:57.0